7%2F12%2F23%2F103434_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=eabf09d5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2649ed6155e79c8d124d0fb19c737b75ff35f9ca","tid":507083,"uid":21761,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-23T03:31:20.000Z","msg":"真 懶係女強人咁款 屌你老母一巴打落去<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8de86b9066505b38a85ae3cef8e123e63455f53d","tid":507083,"uid":152123,"like":55,"dislike":6,"score":49,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-23T03:52:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>真 懶係女強人咁款 屌你老母一巴打落去<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n問親佢哋點解唔留長頭髮 <br />\n就會一下子trigger到佢哋弱小心靈<br />\n佢哋就會起曬鋼<br />\n<br />\n和善答案：<br />\n因為長頭髮好難打理 洗頭好難乾 咁樣舒服啲<br />\n<br />\n激進答案：<br />\n點解女人一定要長頭髮啊？女人都可以短頭髮架喎<br />\n長頭髮先至靚架咩？短頭髮都可以好靚架喎<br />\n你睇啊邊個邊個明星（中女愛指梁詠琪） 咪又係短髮 都好睇吖<br />\n最緊要適合自己個性 襯得好睇咪得囉"},{"pid":"5e5d19f5568be258a1999dd49a250a624d32cbcd","tid":507083,"uid":152123,"like":22,"dislike":1,"score":21,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-23T03:54:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>唔覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 留到好長個啲女先恐怖<br />\n好多份人好撚假<br />\n對住你笑騎騎，轉過頭周圍唱你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n通常短頭髮女仔份人真啲<br />\n有咩會照直講，可能咁你會覺得西<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但都好過啲人前人後兩個樣啲臭西</blockquote>樓主話短髮閪啫 冇話長髮唔閪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n大部份女人都長頭髮 有某班人西<br />\n好難話大部份長頭髮女都係西<br />\n<br />\n但超短髮女本身都已經少 仲要西嘅佔咗入面大比數"},{"pid":"72c1a42ac03cd75acc4eef652df46119b4298fa5","tid":507083,"uid":116560,"like":48,"dislike":4,"score":44,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-23T04:12:43.000Z","msg":"長頭髮又唔得 短頭髪又唔得<br />\n全部光頭好唔好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n